<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti samasta guṇagaṇālaṁkāra
<lb n="2"/>vigaliḍa madakaladviṣadahaṁkāra
<lb n="3"/>pa hiṁḍipālakula kulācala mi
<lb n="4" break="no"/>gēṁda caturtthakulakumudinī caṁdra
<lb n="5"/>Aribirudamadadviradamadanivāraṇa
<lb n="6"/>goṁka narēṁdra gandhavāraṇa tanaruṁba ṟī
<lb n="7" break="no"/>dipuravarādhīśvara samabhyarccita trikō
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭīśvara vivaraṇa raṇavinōda saṁpādi
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ta budha pamōda dipakṣavakṣasthala
<lb n="10" break="no"/>da lanabhalla gaḍigōṭamalla sujana jana
<lb n="11" break="no"/>vada vasaṁtakāṁtājayaṁta gaṁḍara
<lb n="12" break="no"/>gaṁḍa gaṁḍamārttaṁḍa nāmādi sa<unclear>masta</unclear> 
</p>

